text: Gintautas Paluckas (; born 19 August 1979) is a Lithuanian politician. He has been the 18th and current Prime Minister of Lithuania since 2024. Paluckas was Deputy Mayor of Vilnius from 2015 to 2019. He was the leader of the Lithuanian Social Democratic Party (LSDP) from 2017 to 2021. ==References== Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:Current national leaders Category:Prime ministers of Lithuania Category:Politicians from Vilnius
